#11201
Preface~
   On the outskirts of Midgaard stands a mighty fortress, over which
flies a banner marked with a blazing phoenix.  In this fabled citadel
dwell the Kai, an elite order of knights who daily dedicate their lives
to upholding the virtues they hold dear.  To be courageous, standing
tall in the face of danger; to be true, to themselves and to others; to
be just in a world that is not; to be honourable, for a life without
honour is not a life at all. Upon these virtues, a fellowship has grown.
The Kai embody all this and more. They are truly a breed apart.
~
