#11202
Prologue~
   A long time ago, in a land far, far away, a band of heroes fled
their world and ventured into the realm of Elite. They brought with
them a set of values and a rich history, that of Kai. Time passed, 
and the heroes went their separate ways.
   A dark time came. A mighty empire rose and fell. The Saracens
were born from the ashes of this empire.  Led by Nymph and Deimos,
this small tribe struggled for survival. Lacking any sense of 
direction or purpose, the tribe nearly faded away, until the Kai, led
by Ben Kenobi and Deimos, took control of the people. Thus the Kai 
was born. The Kai citadel was built around this time.
~
