Chapter One~
   The Kai clan was small at first, a minor power in a world of 
great clans. Many great names of yesteryear helped found the clan.
No one speaks of Toon, Dementor, or Radagast anymore, but these 
were the names that made the clan what it was. With the fall of the 
Pack, heroes such as Viv and Soulcatcher found their way into Kai.
Mighty warriors followed long time friends, and soon the Kai were 
proud to have in their number names such as Zifnab, Dakkon, Karen,
Xala, and many other famous people, too numerous to mention. Kai 
had become a clan without equal.
