#11204
Chapter Two~
   It was not to last. Troublesome elements entered into the clan.
Catwoman and Ashenshugar became two strong supporters within the 
clan, but with time, the friendships that kept them in Kai soured
and decayed. Atlantis, one of our greatest, faded into obscurity,
and the clan found itself at a crossroads. Would it take the path
of power and might, or the path of honor and truth? The clan was 
torn asunder as this decision was made. Those who departed during 
this chaos were many: Zifnab, Dakkon, Karen, Ashenshugar, Rakshar, 
Atlantis, Crimson... for reasons ranging from personal honor to 
conflicts with other members to infractions of clan policy, one bye 
one they left.
